Given $e=1.60 \times 10^{-19} \mathrm{C}$
$$
d=9.17 \times 10^{-11} \mathrm{~m}
$$
From $\mu=e \times d$
$$
\begin{aligned}
\mu & =1.60 \times 10^{-19} \times 9.17 \times 10^{-11} \\
& =14.672 \times 10^{-30}
\end{aligned}
$$
